      <div class="mt-4 pl-7">
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium">1</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Strong thesis statement</span> – Your thesis clearly articulates your main argument about the text's symbolism.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium">2</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Excellent textual evidence</span> – You consistently support your claims with relevant quotations from the text.</p>
