        Opportunities
      </h3>
      <div class="mt-4 pl-7">
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium">1</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Paragraph organization</span> – Try using stronger topic sentences to guide your reader through your argument.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium">2</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-medium">Citation formatting</span> – Review MLA citation guidelines for in-text citations; several are missing page numbers.</p>
